to stay alive and that's all

01:02:21.208 --> 01:02:23.449
that they got in the old days.
 

01:02:23.449 --> 01:02:27.612
Well what's happened to the
price of clothing in the last

01:02:27.612 --> 01:02:28.949
several decades?
 

01:02:28.949 --> 01:02:33.329
No, the price of clothing all
