world.

01:02:42.969 --> 01:02:45.420
The price of clothing has
dropped tremendously as a

01:02:45.420 --> 01:02:47.871
fraction of income,
you always have to do that as a

01:02:47.871 --> 01:02:49.000
fraction of income.
 

01:02:49.000 --> 01:02:52.137
The price of food has dropped
around the world as a fraction

01:02:52.137 --> 01:02:54.811
