for their kids,

01:03:10.460 --> 01:03:14.974
if it's a cost to providing
that now has gone way down as a

01:03:14.974 --> 01:03:16.610
fraction of income.
 

01:03:16.610 --> 01:03:21.148
As I said, often--usually
education is provided free by

01:03:21.148 --> 01:03:26.023
the government and sometimes
healthcare is provided free by

01:03:26.023 --> 01:03:27.619
the government.
 

01:03:27.619 --> 01:03:31.858
It doesn't look like an
economic issue that if you want

01:03:31.858 --> 01:03:36.490
to just have kids the way you
used to have them the cost has

01:03:36.490 --> 01:03:39.710
not risen but the cost has gone
down.

01:03:39.710 --> 01:03:43.358
What has changed is in the
minds of people they now

01:03:43.358 --> 01:03:47.884
perceive that they must provide
for their children a completely

01:03:47.884 --> 01:03:50.550
expand--
different and expanded set of

01:03:50.550 --> 01:03:51.969
goods than previously.
 

01:03:51.969 --> 01:03:56.222
Children have to have the kind
of education that they never had

01:03:56.222 --> 01:03:56.840
before.
 

01:03:56.840 --> 01:04:00.699
They have to have enrichment
activities, all kinds of stuff.

01:04:00.699 --> 01:04:03.983
If you read about China,
I mean it's amazing what

01:04:03.983 --> 01:04:07.949
Chinese--they only have one
child and that child is so over

01:04:07.949 --> 01:04:10.550
