01:04:39.260 --> 01:04:40.809
What were they interested in?
 

01:04:40.809 --> 01:04:44.389
This issue of modernization,
that they're spoiled,

01:04:44.389 --> 01:04:47.070
they realize that,
they were telling me--

01:04:47.070 --> 01:04:49.586
