that they didn't want to have a

01:04:49.586 --> 01:04:51.248
sibling,
they were really enjoying

01:04:51.248 --> 01:04:52.980
getting everything as an only
child,

01:04:52.980 --> 01:04:54.349
and they did not want a sibling.
 

01:04:54.349 --> 01:04:56.099
She's laughing because you know
that story.

01:04:56.099 --> 01:05:00.581
The other side of the coin is,
as the only child they have to

01:05:00.581 --> 01:05:01.329
succeed.
 

01:05:01.329 --> 01:05:04.856
They have to get top grades in
their education,

01:05:04.856 --> 01:05:09.380
so the amount of pressure on
them to work like crazy all the

01:05:09.380 --> 01:05:12.599
time to study,
study, study is severe.

01:05:12.599 --> 01:05:15.143
They were interested
in--largely in the pressures on

01:05:15.143 --> 01:05:16.690
them which they were feeling.
 

01:05:16.690 --> 01:05:19.507
I guess as Presidents of their
student body's they were

01:05:19.507 --> 01:05:22.376
probably overachievers like
crazy and so they would feel

01:05:22.376 --> 01:05:23.889
this pressure enormously.
 

01:05:23.889 --> 01:05:28.097
Then you hear other stories
where kids learn to play this

01:05:28.097 --> 01:05:30.315
game,
so if a parent wants them--why

01:05:30.315 --> 01:05:33.061
