they can both be watching

01:11:51.975 --> 01:11:54.247
television together or they're
not really doing childcare

01:11:54.247 --> 01:11:57.577
they're just with the children,
it's still--it gets to be more

01:11:57.577 --> 01:12:01.710
significant but this is not time
taken away from anything else,

01:12:01.710 --> 01:12:03.850
just the child happens to be
there.

01:12:03.850 --> 01:12:08.398
Now--and this is moderately
stable, it doesn't change

01:12:08.398 --> 01:12:11.458
between '65 and '98,
about the same,

01:12:11.458 --> 01:12:15.220
a little bit different,
