the fraction--either both the

01:12:39.569 --> 01:12:42.939
number and the fraction of women
working between any of these

01:12:42.939 --> 01:12:43.390
ages.
 

01:12:43.390 --> 01:12:45.069
Yet what do you see?
 

01:12:45.069 --> 01:12:49.363
The amount of time that the
