01:12:49.363 --> 01:12:53.806
up from the total during this
period 9 to 10 hours up to like

01:12:53.806 --> 01:12:54.770
14 hours.
 

01:12:54.770 --> 01:12:59.118
That as women go to work they
spend more time with their

01:12:59.118 --> 01:13:01.716
children;
