very skinny on that hypothesis.

01:13:26.800 --> 01:13:30.478
In fact, if you ask your
mothers or any woman that has

01:13:30.478 --> 01:13:33.810
children, what goes away when
they go to work?

01:13:33.810 --> 01:13:36.260
Not childcare.
 

01:13:36.260 --> 01:13:41.024
Leisure time and sleep;
survey after survey says that

01:13:41.024 --> 01:13:45.033
what women do differently when
they work is they get less sleep

01:13:45.033 --> 01:13:46.649
and less leisure time.
 

